Class NoteSet

java.lang.Object
  NoteSet

public class NoteSet
extends Object

Note Set

A set of all the possible Notes in an octave. This includes the 11 standard semitones, as well as their enharmonically equivalent "names" (C# = Db, etc.)

Version:
3.0
Author:
Devon Hubert
